title = "Camera Controls"
content = "[b]For Mouse users:[/b]
[ul]
Use left button to move the farm around the viewport
Use scroll wheel to zoom in & out the farm
[/ul]

[b]For Trackpad users:[/b]
[ul]
Click and grad to move the farm around the viewport
Zooming gesture zooms in & out the farm
[/ul]"
